Progress

Purpose:
- Public-safe progress ledger for MemoryEndpoints.com implementation, verification, deployment, and dogfooding work.

Last verified: 2026-07-09
Memory scope: chronological progress, verification evidence, and current completion boundary.
Public-safe status: safe for source control; contains no credential values.
Update route: append public-safe verified progress here; submit durable summaries to https://memoryendpoints.com/api/matm/memory-events/submit when authenticated.
Source of truth: current repository state, command output, verification reports, Git commits, and `.uai/totem.uai`.
Next action for agents: add concise evidence-backed entries after real verification; do not claim full goal completion without a requirement-by-requirement audit.
Must not expose: raw API keys, bearer tokens, FTP credentials, database passwords, private keys, private handoff payloads, raw one-time keys, or unredacted deployment handoff values.

